The paper deals with the problem of handwritten character recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques such as classifier combination and statistical significance testing, which are relevant to subcategories such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
